  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK778">
<l>uṟiṉuyi rañcā maṟava riṟaivaṉ</l>
<l>ceyiṉuñcīr kuṉṟa lilar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The heroes who are not afraid of losing their life in a contest will not cool their ardour, even if the king prohibits (their fighting).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
